      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TWO FISTED (1) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten a neck, (20.09) at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Must come into calculations. NANNY'S BOY (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.20) at this track behind Rapid Lulu in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Comes through a solid form race last start. Leading chance. MISS TWIX (8) is having her first look at this circuit. In the money last start when third (17.92) at Taree Super Track over 300m. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Leading player again. ROCKY PEPPER (7) found the frame here last start and looks a top-three hope again.",
